        <h2 id="hd_id3147573">Increase Paragraph Spacing</h2>
        <paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3150695">Increases the paragraph spacing above the selected paragraph.</paragraph>
        <h2 id="hd_id3147574">Decrease Paragraph Spacing</h2>
        <paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3150696">Decreases the paragraph spacing above the selected paragraph.</paragraph>
        <h2 id="hd_id3147575">Increase Indent</h2>
        <paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3150697">Increases the left indent of the current paragraph or cell content and sets it to the next default tab position. If several paragraphs are selected, the indentation of all selected paragraphs is increased.</paragraph>
        <h2 id="hd_id3147576">Decrease Indent</h2>
        <paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3150698">Decreases the left indent of the current paragraph or cell content and sets it to the previous default tab position. If you previously increased the indentation for several collectively selected paragraphs, this command can decrease the indentation for all of the selected paragraphs.</paragraph>
